17:["$","ol","ol-0",{"children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Rupees (Wealth Creation)"}],": Generating ethical, sustainable profit through Zero Defect, Zero Effect methodologies."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Respect (Self and Others)"}],": Cultivating an environment where every stakeholder feels valued."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Relation (Connection)"}],": Building deep, meaningful relationships with family, employees, and society."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-3",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Rest (Rejuvenation)"}],": Prioritizing Dhyan (meditation) and Swadhyaya (self-study) to recharge the mind and soul."]}],"\n"]}]
