19:["$","p","p-4",{"children":["Start your day not with your email inbox, but with 20 minutes of silence. Ask yourself: ",["$","em","em-0",{"children":"Am I chasing profit out of fear, or out of purpose?"}]," When your mind is in a state of Zero (Zero Mind), defects in your product and your life naturally fall away."]}]
